snippet.title: Dungeon Gals - SAGE 2024 Trailer (Demo Available!)
snippet.description:
SAGE 2024 is here, and Dungeon Gals is a part of it!

You can download a playable demo with the link below, with it containing two areas from the game. That might not sound like a lot, but you'd be surprised just how much there is to do!

If you enjoy the demo, please leave a positive comment and share it around! It helps a ton.

https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/dungeon-gals.2305/
